    | GetAllAuthors
    -- | OnLocationChange Navigation.Location
    | GoToEditor
    | GoToReader
    | GoToNewDocument
    | GoToLogin

    | UpdateSelectedDocument String

    | InputTitle String
    | InputAuthor String
